Package: DPprior
Title: Dirichlet Process Prior Elicitation
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("JoonHo", "Lee", , "jlee296@ua.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0006-4019-8703"))
Description: Provides calibration tools for the concentration parameter of
    Dirichlet process priors, enabling principled prior specification
    through cluster count and weight distribution targets. Implements
    closed-form approximations and exact numerical methods for mapping
    user beliefs about expected cluster counts to Gamma hyperparameters.
